"title": "4150: cherubim",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4150",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Winged, heavenly creatures represented in the tabernacle and the temple.</p>\n<h2>Description of the cherubim</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:12-Ezek10:14\">EZK 10:12–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:4-Ezek1:14\">EZK 1:4–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:22-Ezek1:24\">EZK 1:22–1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:5\">EZK 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:8\">EZK 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:21-Ezek10:22\">EZK 10:21–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:18-Ezek41:19\">EZK 41:18–41:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:6-Rev4:8\">REV 4:6–4:8</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim represented in the tabernacle and the temple</h2>\n<h3>Cherubim as decorations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8\">EXO 36:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:29\">1KI 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a></p>\n<h3>Cherubim at the entrance to the inner sanctuary</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:31-Exod26:33\">EXO 26:31–26:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:35\">EXO 36:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:32\">1KI 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:14\">2CH 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Cherubim over the ark of the covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:5\">HEB 9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:17-Exod25:22\">EXO 25:17–25:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:7-Exod37:9\">EXO 37:7–37:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:89\">NUM 7:89</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:23-1Kgs6:28\">1KI 6:23–6:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:10-2Chr3:13\">2CH 3:10–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:6-1Kgs8:7\">1KI 8:6–8:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:7-2Chr5:8\">2CH 5:7–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:18\">1CH 28:18</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim represented in Ezekiel's vision of the temple</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:18\">EZK 41:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:20\">EZK 41:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:25\">EZK 41:25</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim represent the place of God's throne</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:4\">1SA 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:2\">2SA 6:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:6\">1CH 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:15\">2KI 19:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:16\">ISA 37:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1\">PSA 80:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:1\">PSA 99:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:1\">EZK 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:6\">REV 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:6\">REV 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim as guardians</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:24\">GEN 3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:14\">EZK 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:16\">EZK 28:16</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim as God's chariot</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:11\">2SA 22:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:10\">PSA 18:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:18\">1CH 28:18</a></p>\n<h2>Cherubim as agents of judgment</h2>\n<h3>Cherubim remove God's glory</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:3-Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:3–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:15-Ezek10:19\">EZK 10:15–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:22-Ezek11:23\">EZK 11:22–11:23</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment poured out</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:2\">EZK 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:6-Ezek10:7\">EZK 10:6–10:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:1-Rev6:8\">REV 6:1–6:8</a> <em>the living creatures release the four horsemen of God's judgment on earth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:7\">REV 15:7</a></p>",
